## TAILWIND SETUP

- Version: Tailwind v4
- In v4, colors MUST be declared via `@theme inline` in `globals.css` — `tailwind.config.ts` does NOT generate utility classes for colors
- `darkMode: ["class", "[data-theme='dark']"] as const` in `tailwind.config.ts`
- Dark mode is handled by `next-themes` via the `"class"` strategy
- The `.dark` class on `<html>` activates the dark token overrides in `globals.css`

